      • LargeVehicle

        public LargeVehicle(int typeIndicator,
                    java.lang.String model,
                    java.lang.String licensePlate,
                    java.lang.String color,
                    Client owner,
                    int spot,
                    int stayIndicator,
                    int numberOfTime)
        This is the main constructor of the class.
        Parameters:
        typeIndicator - The index that represents the type of the vehicle being instantiated. Must be between 0 and 4.
        model - The model of the vehicle being instantiated. @NotEmpty.
        licensePlate - The license plate of the vehicle. @NotEmpty.
        color - The color of the vehicle. @NotEmpty.
        owner - The client that owns the vehicle. @NotNull.
        spot - The index of the spot where the vehicle will be slotted. Must be between -10 and 29.
        stayIndicator - The index that represents the stay type of the vehicle. Must be between 0 and 3.
        numberOfTime - The amount of time the vehicle will stay inside of the parking lot. The units are given by the stayIndicator. @NotNeg.
